This program Code for Molecular Mechanics and Molecular Dynamics (CM3D)
performs Moleculare Dynamics (MD) simulations.

To compile the code choose the correct makefile that fit your needs.
Then type make -f <makefile>.  If all goes well you should have an executable
in the compile directory.  

There are a few examples of in the examples directory with all the
files that you need.  

To run the code 
./executable input.file


